  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "3b8fda53d36be9b1c615393022854a5d54962b929af52b71c54afa245993cf9a": "'We', [?]?",
    "0ee7833dfd8f4ca93e6346a121611963625a1e047d8fba61878f1e4be5555ec4": "All is not well, [?]. Despite having had Glough under close surveillance since the events on Ape Atoll, he has managed to escape the Stronghold.",
    "e5c44078402b1180da2567b3651dea90f47f6eba54225c5f87567bdf9922c6ae": "How are you getting on, [?]?",
    "509cead59463f9b74d19b2b72814e8d7f2e031b6ae6b74ab11228293c5d37b0e": "[?], you must find out where Glough might have travelled to. Assistant Lori may be able to help.",
    "edd1da9f8cbb71001e60dead950e33a0c053e1953bf68aaef111986bddd6e67e": "Have you been able to find out where Glough has gone, [?]",
    "172c524052f5b6aae9220fa785496d059f09f349c60cb9c6ce668d928e097ed7": "Please hurry, [?]. Glough is very dangerous and must be stopped!",
    "729f59571cebb1a224411b244c90af557e17654fc9a1387d6a211cd9c2336a28": "Glough is a threat to us all... I must hereby re-assign you to Ape Atoll, [?]. Report to Sergeant Garkor on Ape Atoll for further orders.",
    "4a3d0e52b9e8e48ee9a638661098cf3a351d46bbdacb9fd32388769fee675a04": "I have given you orders, [?]. Report to Sergeant Garkor on Ape Atoll for further instruction.",
    "b13c6c4b199e1ad81ecc6a10134681d85a8cd439e1ef270fc107823e0d3a0afa": "How is the mission going, [?]?",
    "d0a4672a8eb1441afd052c45cd64d9318e2ec35edf3c75517b869dcf41c9d1c2": "Get Nieve and defend the Stronghold, [?]!",
    "a56f5a9fdbc27326ebdab0be9305788ab83e4c559d9eee60e748e2e1018a97da": "Good work, [?], my troops can take it from here. You and Nieve should investigate the crash site.",
    "6fbca106e546d511953d6f6c0423443a4a12f49256b1dd945dd5e8d8e0f2cb99": "This is excellent news, [?]. Where is Nieve?",
    "619448aabe293a29e804505e8149638812a5a9227e51c769e3ed292afd189e03": "Rest, [?], you have earned it. I will have you summoned when the peace agreement is complete, you should be present during a moment of such historic importance.",
    "0af53c7d8205d7d667bc052cac40911bff382643ac8d2b706d03d89424473133": "On behalf of the Gnomes I can only thank you, [?].",
    "f1dfd1394dcb02d9403b9f6f94c29d0282ecda7d0bc37a103383e8734de4e9f9": "Good to see you again, [?].",
    "967810cdd4715c1755a011282aa9ecee3ba7bb2687b66f7b87df6a647069a4e9": "All is well in the Stronghold thanks to you, [?]."
  }
}